title: Hour 1 - Chris Haynes (06-17-20)
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Chris Haynes (06-17-20)
description:
Chris Haynes tells Dan that for the NBA; the Orlando plan is the best for the safety of the players. Chris said that players were hesitant due to the covid-19, but now some players are concerned that playing will distract from the Black Lives Matter Movement.
